node.text:
Today was very unfortunate

The incident could have been avoided if I had been left enough space to make the corner. You need 2 people to make that work and I feel I was squeezed out of it

When racing each other, these things can happen, unfortunately

node.text:
A good start gives us pole for the race and 2️⃣ more points

It will be another interesting battle tomorrow ⚔️🦁🇮🇹
 
And yes, very happy with the first medal in my life 🥈😉

This is never an easy track for us, so starting from the second row means there’s all to play for 💪🇮🇹

node.text:
Still enjoying yesterday, but already looking ahead to Monza. And to arrive in Italy in style, I’ve asked Alpha Tauri Fashion to help me out 

But after the amazing win in Zandvoort, they came with a special surprise for all my fans to celebrate this special moment together 🏆

If you head over to the Alpha Tauri website, you can use discount code ‘MAX33’ for 33% off on selected products

More info 👉 link in bio
